15:13.340 --> 15:14.702
Yeah, right.

15:14.722 --> 15:17.044
I think it's part of this, he's digitized.

15:17.064 --> 15:18.345
He bought the Bettman Archive.

15:18.405 --> 15:19.326
Yes.

