15:23.363 --> 15:24.224
Very interesting.

15:24.364 --> 15:24.884
I called him.

15:24.904 --> 15:26.326
He must be a remarkable guy.

15:26.346 --> 15:29.689
Yes, he sounds so lucid and clear, and he's in a retirement home.

15:29.969 --> 15:31.110
Yeah.

15:31.190 --> 15:32.671
And I said, what day is good?

15:32.691 --> 15:34.913
He says, I'm here all the time.

15:35.134 --> 15:35.594
He's coming.

15:35.794 --> 15:36.054
Right.

15:36.155 --> 15:38.016
I'm looking forward to your arrival.

15:39.157 --> 15:39.257
Yeah.

15:39.277 --> 15:45.543
